<body onload="SignupForm_AuthUser('<%= @authCode %>', '<%= @companyName %>', '<%= @incorporationType %>', '<%= @bussStreetAddress %>', '<%= @bussCity %>', '<%= @bussState %>', '<%= @bussZipCode %>', '<%= @mailStreetAddress %>', '<%= @mailCity %>', '<%= @mailState %>', '<%= @mailZipCode %>', '<%= @phoneNumber %>', '<%= @email %>', '<%= @license %>');">
	<div id="wrapper">
	<div id="header-wrapper">
		<div class="browser-center">
        	<div id="header-area">
            	<div id="logo"><a href="/"><%= image_tag("logo.jpg", :alt => "") %></a></div>
                <div id="facebook-like"><%= image_tag("facebook-like.jpg", :alt => "") %></div>
                <div id="customer-support">
                	<p>Customer Support</p>
                    <h1>703 555 5555</h1>
                    <p>Any Questions <a href="mailto:">Email Us</a></p>
                </div>
                <div id="navigation">
                	<div id="nav">
                    	<ul>
                        	<li class="first"><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">About BillysList</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">How it works </a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">FAQ’s</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Testimonials</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Press Release</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                	<div class="login-wrapper">
                		<div  class="login-register"><a href="#">Login/Register</a></div>
                    	<div id="signin_menu">    
                    		<p>                
                      		<label for="username">Username or email</label>
                      		<input id="username" name="username" value="" title="username" tabindex="4" type="text">
                      		</p>
                      		<p>
                        	<label for="password">Password</label>
                        	<input id="password" name="password" value="" title="password" tabindex="5" type="password">
                      		</p>
                      		<p class="remember">
                        	<input id="signin_submit" value="Sign in" tabindex="6" type="submit">
                        	<input id="remember" name="remember_me" value="1" tabindex="7" type="checkbox">
                        	<label for="remember">Remember me</label>
                      		</p>
                      		<p class="forgot"> <a href="#" id="resend_password_link">Forgot your password?</a> </p>
                      		<div class="signup">New User? <a href="/user_registeration/GetRegister">Signup Here</a></div>                                          
                    	</div>
                   	</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="banner">
        	<div class="browser-center">
            	<div id="banner-area">
                	<div class="banner-content">
                    	<h1>Lorem Ipsum, consectetur, adipisci</h1>
                        <p>If you want to know about your customer that he will pay for the quality services that you provide. BillysList is the right tool to confirm.</p>
                        <p><a href="#">More Information</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="search">
                    	<form action="/customer_search/GetDetails" method="post">
                    	<div class="search-heading">Search Customer Rate/Reviews or Search for info on a potential customer.</div>
                    	<div id="search-form">
                        	<div class="form-textbox">
                        	  <input name="txtFirstName" type="text" required="true" class="textbox-small" id="txtFirstName" placeholder="First Name" />
                        	</div>
                        	<div class="form-textbox">
                        	  <input name="txtLastName" type="text" required="true" class="textbox-small" id="txtLastName" placeholder="Last Name" />
                        	</div>
                            <div class="form-textbox">
                        	  <input name="txtStreetAddress" type="text" required="true" class="textbox" id="txtStreetAddress" placeholder="Street Address" />
                        	</div>
                          	<div class="form-textbox">
                       	    	<input name="selectCity" type="text" required="true" autocomplete="off" class="textbox" id="selectCity" placeholder="City, State" />
                        	
                       	    	<!--<select name="selectCity" id="selectCity" class="dropdown">
                        	    	<option>City</option>
                        	    	<% @city=City.find(:all)%>
                        	    	<% @city.each do |incity| %>
										<option><%= incity.Name %></option>
									<% end %>
                      	      </select>-->
                        	</div>
                        	<div class="form-textbox">
                        	<!--<input name="selectState" type="text" required="true" class="textbox" id="selectState" placeholder="State" />
                        	
                       	    <select name="selectState" id="selectState" class="dropdown">
                        	    <option>State</option>
                        	    <% @state=State.find(:all)%>
                        	    <% @state.each do |instate| %>
									<option><%= instate.Name %></option>
								<% end %>
                      	     </select>-->
                        	</div>
                            <div class="form-textbox">
                        	  <input name="txtZipCode" type="text" required="true" class="textbox-small" id="txtZipCode" placeholder="Zipcode" />
                        	</div>
                            <div class="form-textbox">
                        	  <input name="txtPhoneNumber" type="text" required="true" class="textbox-small" id="txtPhoneNumber" placeholder="Phone Number" />
                        	</div>
                            <div class="form-textbox">
                       	  	  <input type="submit" name="Submit" id="Submit" value="Submit" class="search-bt" />
                        	</div>
                        	</form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    <div id="main-content-wrapper">
    	<div class="browser-center">
        	<div id="signup-wrapper">
               <div id="signup-header">
                  <h1>Register with us</h1>
                  <h2>Sign-up in just a few easy steps</h2>
               </div>
               <!--<div class="steps"><%= image_tag("step1.jpg", :alt => "") %></div>-->
               
               <div id="singup-form-area">
               		<div class="singup-form-heading">
                    	<h1>Create Your Account</h1>
                        <p>Fill the basic information below to create your account</p>
                        <div id="Error"><%= @messageString %></div>        
                    </div>
                    
               		<div class="singup-form">
               			<div id="chkCodeBox">
                        	<input type="checkbox" id="chkCode" name="chkCode" onclick="SignupForm_visibility(this);" value="1" /> I have company authorization code.                        	                       	               			
                        </div>
               			<div id="SignupCode">
               				<form action="/user_registeration/GetRegister" method="post">
               				<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  		<input type="text" name="textCode" id="textCode" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small" placeholder="Authorization Code" />
                    		</div>
                    		<div class="singup-textarea">
                        		<input type="submit" name="Submit" id="Submit" value="Submit" class="org-bt" />
                        	</div>
                        	</form>                        
                        </div>
                        <div id="SignupReadOnlyCode">
               				<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  		<input type="text" name="textFilledCode" required="true" id="textFilledCode" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Authorization Code" />
                    		</div>
                    		<div class="singup-textarea">
                        		<a href="#" onclick="Change_CheckCode();">Change Authorization Code</a>
                        	</div>
                        </div>
               			<div id="SignupForm">
               			<form action="/user_registeration/GetRegister" method="post">
               			<input type="hidden" id="hiddenFilledCode" name="hiddenFilledCode" />
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textCompany" id="textCompany" required="true" class="singup-textbox"  placeholder="Name of Company" value="<%= params[:textCompany] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textFirstName" id="textFirstName" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Owner First Name" value="<%= params[:textFirstName] %>" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                          <input type="text" name="textLastName" id="textLastName" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Owner Last Name" value="<%= params[:textLastName] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textIncorporationType" id="textIncorporationType" required="true" class="singup-textbox"  placeholder="Type of Incorporation" value="<%= params[:textIncorporationType] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textBussStreetAddress" required="true" id="textBussStreetAddress" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Business Street Address" value="<%= params[:textBussStreetAddress] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textBussCity" id="textBussCity" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="City" value="<%= params[:textBussCity] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textBussState" id="textBussState" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="State" value="<%= params[:textBussState] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textBussZipCode" id="textBussZipCode" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="ZipCode" value="<%= params[:textBussZipCode] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    		<input type="checkbox" id="chkAddress" name="chkAddress" value="1" onclick="check_chkAddress(this);" /> Use Business Address as Mailing Address.
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textMailStreetAddress" id="textMailStreetAddress" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Mailing Street Address" value="<%= params[:textMailStreetAddress] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textMailCity" id="textMailCity" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="City" value="<%= params[:textMailCity] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textMailState" id="textMailState" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="State" value="<%= params[:textMailState] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textMailZipCode" id="textMailZipCode" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="ZipCode" value="<%= params[:textMailZipCode] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textPhoneNumber" id="textPhoneNumber" required="true" class="singup-textbox"  placeholder="Phone Number" value="<%= params[:textPhoneNumber] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="email" name="textEmail" id="textEmail" required="true" onchange="form.textConfirmEmail.pattern = this.value;" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Email Address" value="<%= params[:textEmail] %>" />
                          </div>
                          <div class="singup-textarea">
                          <input type="email"  name="textConfirmEmail" id="textConfirmEmail" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Confirm Email Address" value="<%= params[:textConfirmEmail] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textLicense" id="textLicense" required="true" class="singup-textbox"  placeholder="Contractor License Number" value="<%= params[:textLicense] %>" />
                    	</div>
                    	<div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="text" name="textUserName" id="textUserName" required="true" class="singup-textbox"  placeholder="User Name" value="<%= params[:textUserName] %>" />
                    	</div>
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                    	  <input type="password" name="textPassword" id="textPassword" required="true" onchange="form.textConfirmPassword.pattern = this.value;" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Password" />
                          </div>
                          <div class="singup-textarea">
                          <input type="password"  name="textConfirmPassword" id="textConfirmPassword" required="true" class="singup-textbox-small"  placeholder="Confirm Password" />
                    	</div>
                    	<input type="hidden" id="hiddenPrice" name="hiddenPrice" />
                        <div class="singup-textarea">
                        	<input type="submit" name="Submit" id="Submit" value="Save & Continue" class="org-bt" />
                        </div>
                        </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               
             </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="footer-wrapper">
    	<div class="browser-center">
        	<div class="footer-links">
            	<ul>
                	<li><a href="<%= root_path %>">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">About BillysList</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">How it works</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">FAQ’s</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Testimonials</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Press Release</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright">Copyright © 2013. All Right Reserved. <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>   |   <a href="#">Terms & Conditions</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
</body>
</html>
